{"tid":792617,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★【$300】申請表格曝光　建制組織派錢席捲觀塘區","createTime":"2018-08-24T16:32:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T16:44:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4d0c8235bd5ff6a2dd5de124e145efa229a7c969","tid":792617,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T16:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1783380/org/5eb8602a6d4a58d652f25ab6babba6b4.jpeg/yCZEfGViMWfEvas_RTKANAGYd2HLREb3tDewrLQ3sKw?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1783380%2Forg%2F5eb8602a6d4a58d652f25ab6babba6b4.jpeg%2FyCZEfGViMWfEvas_RTKANAGYd2HLREb3tDewrLQ3sKw%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=332a6dec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1786737/org/f30091917c4e592c80c894bb7ce09e1d.jpg/n2CW9E6-83V_uoL82KJpZOvz_n4IeGWzZFMo32RTKN8?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1786737%2Forg%2Ff30091917c4e592c80c894bb7ce09e1d.jpg%2Fn2CW9E6-83V_uoL82KJpZOvz_n4IeGWzZFMo32RTKN8%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=b24fd4fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1786635/org/4c13e45d9a4dd5a9137597871be18302.jpg/3CID9iU7itt5xXZgI-_5aEq_CpI6ZEegonnU5aJ51OU?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1786635%2Forg%2F4c13e45d9a4dd5a9137597871be18302.jpg%2F3CID9iU7itt5xXZgI-_5aEq_CpI6ZEegonnU5aJ51OU%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=37f030b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該街坊指，每年近開學時期，都會有組織舉辦相關計劃，但都只是派派文具包，從來未見過有組織直接派錢。<br />\n<br />\n記者曾以市民身份，致電宣傳單張上觀塘民聯會的電話，查詢有關單張的真偽，以及津貼的申請方法。雖然單張似是未完成的草稿，但職員指，該為真的單張，而申請津貼需填妥表格，惟有關表格並無電子版，申請者須親身到其會址領取。<br />\n<br />\n職員表示，不止和樂邨邨民合資格申請，凡住在觀塘區的居民，都可申領有關津貼。居民只需提供學生手冊，以作核實，而因手冊上有地址，故不用再額外提供住址證明。申請資格亦無對家庭背景或成績作出限制或審核，而名額有限，將以抽籤方式決定誰會<span style=\"color: red;\">得到300元的津貼</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/226630/%E8%9B%87%E9%BD%8B%E9%A4%85%E7%B3%AD%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A-%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2%E5%B8%AD%E6%8D%B2%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E5%8D%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F226630%2F%25E8%259B%2587%25E9%25BD%258B%25E9%25A4%2585%25E7%25B3%25AD%25E5%258D%2587%25E7%25B4%259A-%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%258C%25A2%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E6%258D%25B2%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598%25E5%258D%2580&d=%2F1M2ukkmkj5ThbwnWyB%2Behxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=2b9de751\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/226630/%E8%9B%87%E9%BD%8B%E9%A4%85%E7%B3%AD%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A-%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2%E5%B8%AD%E6%8D%B2%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E5%8D%80</a>"},{"pid":"3030765c76d2a08274672326ac3b9ca8d0feb57a","tid":792617,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T16:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0bbc5c751824171d973c5a7afa59a9edecf8e7","tid":792617,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3030765c76d2a08274672326ac3b9ca8d0feb57a","tid":792617,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T16:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj